\id COL Reconstructed from Ventura Publisher
\h Korosi
\toc1 Khe Por KorosiŇč Ndi Khergi Gap
\toc2 Korosi
\toc3 Kor
\mt1 KOROSI
\mt2 Khe Por KorosiŇč Ndi Khergi Gap
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Korosi, ana Esia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain ki Ňčgu bak…® mbe ma. Ana Efesus Ňčgu bak…®me hara ki. Por nduara Korosi Ňčgu bak…®men sios khavgi fhuvara. Ana khaŇč muuŇčgi, ana Efesusan kav, gumgi mbari ga sarigim, mbe Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara mbuav, ana buni vhuuiŇč ndiav mba fhaiŇč ga ruigi. Mbe rua vov vh…®ra Korosin vegi.
\ip Por kama mueŇč mbararagim, gumgi mbari, mbe Korosin guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mbe nd…®knd…®gi Ňčgim, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®gi pham vui. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbararagiap, kha gava khergiap, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®gi havhar…® zav mba gavar mbe ndi mbarigi. Ana mba gava khergiap, mbe ndi mbav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, Krais, ana za kha bigi gari guman pan ma. Krais nduara taagip nza ndigirga. Nza harigi tuavi z…®n Ňčg…®rga nta nzan kurarga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mba tuavi, nza nta z…®n Ňčg…®rga, nza Krais thav, samra Ňčg…®g…®rga. Fhe Bak…®me Kraisan panan, ana za kha bigi ga muuŇčgi. Kraisan panan Fhe Bak…®me taagip za kha bigi ndir zav mbui. Krais nzan vhen kim, nza t…®vir Ňčkaa z…®n vui. Nza Krais t…®vira z…®n vui.
\ip Por kha gava khergiap, guma phuni ga n…®…®Ňčgim, mani ana ndigap, Korosin vugi. Tikikus gum Onesimus, mani mba gava ndigap vugi. Kha guma Onesimus, Por Firemon ndi gava kherav, ana ana nzuav buni vh…®rver Firemon ga suaŇčgi.
\c 1
\ms1 Krais, ana za kha bigir pan ma. Fhe Bak…®me k…®r…® t…®vi gum anan t…®vi guigira ana ki.
\p 
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt Ef 1.1\x*\x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt Ro 1.7\x*Gu Por, gu Krais Zisas farasarigi Ňčaara guma. Ana vuzvugar, Fhe Bak…®me anan Ňčaarar muun zav nan farasarigi. Na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma Timoti, Ňčka kha gava khergiap, nde Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi, nde Korosi Ňčgu bak…®men kav, nza phorgap guigira Krais khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui. Ňäka kha gavar nde ndi mbai. Nza Ndia Fhe Bak…®me fura nden korar muuŇčv, ndava m…®…®t…®gar nden n…®…®Ňčrim, nde k…®ri.
\s1 Mbe KorosiŇč, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Ef 1.15-16; Fi 1.3; Fm 1.5; Hi 6.10\x*Nza nde nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, nza zazera nde nd…®knd…®gap, anan ndikndigap ana phorga nzuai. Ana nza bak…®me Zisas Kraisan Ndia ma.
\v 4-6 \x - \xo 1:4-6 \xt 2 T 4.8; 1 Pi 1.4\x*\x - \xo 1:4-6 \xt Mk 4.8; 16.15; Zo 15.16; Ef 3.2; 1 Pi 5.12\x*Nza khaŇč muuŇčgiap, nden kameŇč mbararagi. Nde Zisas Kraisan buna vhuueŇč nden h…®gim, nde ne mbararagiap, nde Fhe Bak…®me nden mbuigi bigir vhuuiŇč, nta Hevenan ki, nde ne khoth…®gap, nde nta ndirgen rarga ki. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde guigira Krais Zisas khoth…®gap, nde wari wo ndavir za mba Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®v, wari ki. Mbe za kha nuianan mba buna vhuueŇč bun nzuaim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve mba buna vhuueŇč khoth…®gap, ne z…®n vov, mben t…®vi nzerigi. Mba khesharigi t…®vara nden r…®gar h…®gi. Nde fharigi raara, nde Zisas Kraisan buna vhuueŇč mbararagiap, nde guigira Fhe Bak…®me fhura nde kora muuŇčgi kora muumbara kaŇčgi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Kor 4.12; Fm 1.23\x*Epafras mba buna vhuuen nde kh…®vim, nde ne kaŇčgi. Epafras, ana Kraisan Ňčaara guman vhuuŇč ma. Ana nza phorga Ňčgari guma ma, nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap, guigira ana vuzvugi. Ana nzan kurkurav, Kraisan Ňčaara vhuuŇčra mbui.
\v 8 Ana nde Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi, nde guigira wari won ndavi ndi mbe nd…®…®i t…®v, ana ne bun nza suaŇčgi. Mba t…®v, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nduara mba t…®var nde n…®…®Ňčgi.
\s1 Por havharar Korosin n…®…®n zav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Zo 15.16; Ro 12.2; 1 Ko 1.5; Ef 1.8-9; 1.15-17; 2.10; 4.1; 5.10; 5.17; Fi 1.9; 1.27; 1 Te 4.1; Hi 13.21\x*Nza fharigi raar, nza nde mbui t…®va vhuun kameŇč mbararagiap, nza zazera nden kurkura zav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Ana nden kurkurarim, nde tuituigip ana vuzvuk kaŇčgirga. Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kaŇčgirga, nd…®knd…®gi gum nd…®knd…®gi vhuuin za nden n…®…®Ňčrim, nta guigira nden k…®rga.
\v 10 MaaŇč muuŇčgirga, nde guigira Guma Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi rui t…®var muunga, ana guigira nde mbui t…®vi, ana za nta vuzvugirga. Nde mbark…®rga Ňčaarir vhuuiŇč, nde ntan muunga. Nde maaŇč muuŇčv, tuituigip Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgip, mba nd…®knd…®k khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, Ňčg…®v, k…®vgirga.
\v 11-12 \x - \xo 1:11-12 \xt Ef 1.11; 1.18-19; 3.16; 4.2\x*Nza Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, nza kha suambara mbui, ana won ŇčkasŇčkar vhuuŇč bak…®men, ana za mbar k…®rga ŇčkasŇčkagir nden n…®…®nga, nde th…®g…® havhargip, simt…®gi ndiv, mbarav k…®v, mba simt…®gi gan…®rim, nta Ňčg…®v vh…®z…®rga. Nde ndikndig…®p, Dara phorg…® suaŇčv, anan ndikndig…®rga. Ana nden kurkurigim, nde t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n vui. Nde maaŇč mbuim, ana nden mbuigi bigir vhuuiŇč, nde nta ndirga. Nde Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi phorg…®p mba bigi ndirga. Nde mba gumgi gu mbigi phorg…®p Fhe Bak…®men, vhava Ňčaarar k…®rga.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Ru 22.53; Ef 2.2; 1 Te 2.12; 2 Pi 1.11\x*Nza fhum g…®ng…®na ŇčkasŇčkar vhen kim, ana g…®ng…®na ŇčkasŇčka vhen taagia nza ndigap, nza ndim, won Kama z…®n fagi. Mba Kam, ana guigira won ndavar ana n…®…®Ňčgi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Ef 1.6-7\x*Fhe Bak…®men Kam, ana taagia nza ndigap, nza muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana nta vh…®zgi.
\s1 Por Krais mbui t…®vi ga nzuav, won Ňčaara nzuai.
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Zo 1.18; 2 Ko 4.4; Hi 1.3\x*Nza guma the Fhe Bak…®me gangirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Fhe Bak…®men Kam, ana ara fara muuŇčgi. Ana Fhe Bak…®men Kama bar ma. Ana za kha Fhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi bigi gari guman pan ma.
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Zo 1.3; 1.10; Ro 8.38; 11.36; Hi 1.2; 2.10; 1 Pi 3.22\x*Mba Kaman farver panan, Fhe Bak…®me kha Hevenan ki bigi ga mbuav, kha nuianan ki bigi ga muuŇčgi. Ana nza kha gari bigi ga mbuav, nza gari fhuv bigi ga muuŇčgi. Nza gari fhuv bigi khare. Ana han enseri havhari, ŇčiniŇčgi havhari, tori gu mbar…®vi, ana za mba bigi ga muuŇčgi. Mba bigi za anan Kaman farver panan h…®gi, ana wo nzuav mba bigi ga muuŇčgi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Zo 1.1-3; 8.58; 17.5; 1 Ko 8.6\x*Mba bigi, nta zumgum h…®gi, Krais fhum ki. Ana mba bigi ga mbuim, anan ŇčkasŇčkar nta nzerara wari wo ki Ňčanin kav, nta wari t…®gap Ňčgari.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt FG 26.23; 1 Ko 15.20; 15.23; Ef 1.10; 1.22-23; VB 1.5\x*Ana siosan pan ma, sios ana khar…®k ma. Ana nduara zazera k…®r…® t…®va vhuun sios ga nd…®…®i n…®…®Ňčge ma. Ana za kha vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi kharav, rimgiap, fharav khavgi guma ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana nduara za kha bigi gari guman pan ma.
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Zo 1.16; 3.34; Kor 2.9\x*Fhe Bak…®me khueŇč vuzvugi, ana k…®r…® t…®v gum anan t…®vi, nta za anan Kaman k…®rga. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me guigira ana phorga ki.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Ro 5.1; 2 Ko 5.18; Ef 1.7; 1.10; 2.13; 2.16; 1 Zo 2.2\x*Fhe Bak…®me za kha nuianan ki bigi gum Hevenan ki bigir muuŇčgirim, nta za ana phorg…®p ndava bavira k…®rgeŇč vuzvugi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap fhura Krais garim, ana khanarareŇč ga ntorgap rimgi. Ana khanarareŇč ga ntorgim, ana v…®z…®n siasuagim, Fhe Bak…®me nza panan ana kegi t…®vi, ana nta mbevigim, nza ana phorgap ndava bavira ki.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Ro 5.10; Ef 2.12; 4.18; Ta 1.15-16\x*Nde fhum Fhe Bak…®me thav samra ki. Nde panan ana kegap, maaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, t…®vi mbat…®gir ana mbui.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Ef 2.14-16; 5.27; 1 Te 4.7; Ta 2.14\x*Krais khanarareŇč ga ntorgap rimgi. Ana mba t…®va muuŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®me nde phorgap ndava bavira ki. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana nde ndigap, won han zi. Nde ana n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®v, ana n…®man simt…®k thueŇč k…®rga fhu.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Mk 16.15; Ef 3.17; 1 T 3.16; Hi 3.14\x*Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va suirav, guigira havhargip th…®g…®ri. Nde muuŇčv k…®rim, big…®n thueŇč nde Ňčg…®rg…®rim, nde mba mbararagi buna vhuueŇč, nde nen rarga ki, nde ne tharga. Gu Por, gu mba buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai Ňčaara guma kav, nza mba buna vhuueŇč bun za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčgi.
\s1 Por Korosin kurkurigi.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Ro 5.3; 2 Ko 1.5-6; Ef 1.23; 3.13; Fi 3.10; 2 T 1.8\x*Gu ntigem, nden kurkurav zaa ndi ne nzuav ndikndigi. Krais won siosan kurkurav ndigi zaagi vh…®zgi fhuvara. Sios, ana Krais khar…®k ma. Ntigem, Kraisan sios mba zaagi ndirga. Gu Kraisan sios f…®ga mueŇč ma. Gu ana siosan kurkurav won fhavara mba zaagi mbari ndi.
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Ef 3.2; 3.7-8\x*Fhe Bak…®me nduara nan farasarigim, gu siosan Ňčaara guma kav, gu nden kurkurigi. Gu guigira za Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun suanga Ňčaar ki.
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt Ro 16.25-26; 1 Ko 2.7; Ef 3.3-5; 3.9-10; 2 T 1.10\x*Fhum tugivigen mba buneŇč zorga kim, mba gumgi gu mbigi mba buneŇč kaŇčgi fhu. Ntigem, mba buneŇč ne guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi n…®man k…®rar h…®gi.
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Ro 9.23; 2 Ko 2.14; Ef 1.18; 3.8; 1 T 1.1\x*Fhe Bak…®me wo vuzvugara, ana mba zorga ki buneŇč, ana nen nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, ana nen nza kh…®vigi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgim, nza kaŇčgi mba buneŇč, ne guigira buna vhuueŇč ma, ne za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigir kurkurarga. Mba zorga ki buneŇč khaŇč muuŇčgi, Krais nde phorga ki. Ana nde ndigirim, nde Ňčg…®p, ana phorg…® k…®v, ana bigir vhuuiŇč nde Hevenan nta ndirga, nde nen rarga ki.
\v 28 \x - \xo 1:28 \xt Ef 4.13; 5.27\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza Kraisan buna vhuueŇč bun za kha gumgi ga nzuai. Nza nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč z…®n vuav, nza mba bunen mbe nzuav mbe kh…®vav, kama havharara mbe nzuai. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nza khueŇč vuzvugi, mbe guigira khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi k…®rga, nza mben kov, Fhe Bak…®me han Ňčg…®rga.
\v 29 \x - \xo 1:29 \xt FG 20.20; 20.27; Ef 3.7; 3.20; Fi 4.13\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Krais na nd…®…®i ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me, gu Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav, mba Ňčaara mbui.
\c 2
\s1 Nza khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip Zisas khoth…®g…®p, mba guiguigi buni, nza nta daaŇčgi mbur kh…®ngirga.
\p 
\v 1 Gu nde khueŇč kaŇčgirgane vuzvugi. Gu khaŇč t…®gap havhargia Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav, nden kurkurav Raodisian siosan ki gumgi gu mbigi, gu mben kurkurav, vh…®ra mba nan khoma gangi fhuv gumgi gu mbigi, gu vh…®ra mben kurkurigi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt 2 Ko 1.6; Ef 3.4; 3.18; Fi 3.8; Kor 1.26; 3.14\x*Gu mba Ňčaara mbuav, gu za mben ndavi havharav, mben ndavi khavi, mbe guigira wari won ndavir warir n…®…®Ňčv, mbe phorg…®p ndava bavira k…®ri. Gu khueŇč vuzvugi, nde nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ndirim, mba nd…®knd…®gi nde Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k havhargirga. Gu vh…®ra khueŇč vuzvugi, nde vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me mba zorgi buneŇč n…®…®eŇč, nde niŇčge kaŇčgirga. Krais, ana nduara mba zorga ki bunen n…®…®eŇč ma.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Ais 45.3; 1 Ko 1.24; 1.30; Ef 1.8; 3.19\x*Mba zorga ki bigi kaŇčgi nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kaŇčgi nd…®knd…®k, nta guigira Kraisan ki. Nta Ňčk…®…®a ki phenan, Ňčk…®…®a guigira ana givav ki fara muuŇčgi.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Ro 16.18; Ef 4.14; 5.6; Kor 2.8\x*Gu guma the nde raaŇč sh…®v, nde guigirga ne vuzvugi fhu. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap kha bunen nde nzuai.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt 1 Ko 5.3; 14.40; 1 Pi 5.9\x*Gu nde phorga ki fhuvara. Gu won nd…®knd…®gar, gu nde phorga ki. Gu nde garim, nde nzerara wari t…®gap khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap Zisas khoth…®gim, gu nde gan…®ngen ndikndigi.
\s1 Nza guigira Krais phorg…®p, nza guigira k…®r…® t…®var vhuuŇč ndigirga.
\p 
\v 6 Nde Guma Bak…®me Krais Zisas ndigi, nde ana phorg…® ruri.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Ef 2.20-22; 3.17; Kor 1.23\x*Nde ana t…® th…®g…®p havhargip, kha nuiana th…®gi farar muuŇčgiri. Nde vh…®ra, phena k…®na havharage t…® th…®gi farar muuŇčgiri. Nde nza mba nde kh…®vav nde suaŇčgi bunan vhuueŇč, nde kha t…®g…®p havhargip, ne khoth…®g…®ri. Nde ne khoth…®g…®p, nde zazera Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčv, ana ndikndig…®ri.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Ga 4.3; 4.9; Ef 5.6; Kor 2.3; 2.18-20; Hi 13.9\x*Nde tuituigira wari gan…®ri. Nde muuŇčv k…®rim, guma the mbark…®rga guiguigi buni k…®ni gum nd…®knd…®gir nde suaŇčv nden muuŇčrim, nde ana nd…®knd…®gi z…®n Ňčgeg…®rga. Mba khesharigi gumgi, mbe wari won nz…®gi gum, kha buip gum, nuiana gari ŇčiniŇčgi gu tori gu mbar…®vi, mbe ntan nd…®knd…®gi z…®n vui. Mbe Krais nd…®knd…®gi z…®n vui fhuvara.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Zo 1.14-16; Kor 1.19\x*Nde kaŇčgi, Krais ana nzara fara muuŇčgiap guma guara gegim, Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi guigira givav anan ki.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Ef 1.21-22\x*Nde Krais nt…®…®ri ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me guigira k…®r…® t…®var vhuun nde n…®…®Ňčgim, mba t…®v guigira nden ki. Ana mba ŇčkasŇčka ki bigi gu tori gu mbar…®vi, ana za ntan ŇčkasŇčka mbevigim, nta za vergi. Ntan ŇčkasŇčka, ana ŇčkasŇčka kambararga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nta ana piin kim, anan ŇčkasŇčka mbe gari.
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Ro 2.29\x*Nde ana phorga kav, nde guigira warir fooi t…®va ndigi. Mba t…®v, ana nde fhura wari wo fhavi ga mbui t…®v fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nza Krais t…®vi z…®n vov, nza wari won ndava vura t…®vi, nza nta vharigim, nta nza thav sagi. Mba t…®v, ana guigira fooi t…®va guar ma.
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Ro 6.4; Ef 1.19-20; 3.7; Kor 3.1\x*Nde ndavi dorgap, nde Zisas phorgap ruagim, Fhe Bak…®me nde ndiv, Krais phorgap mboga t…®gi, nde rimgi. Krais rimgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana khavgim, nde Fhe Bak…®me ŇčkasŇčka khoth…®gap, ruagim, ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap taagia Krais khavav, ana vh…®ra nde khavgi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Ef 2.1-5\x*Nde fhum mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, nde vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me gumgi ki fhuvara, nde maaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde vh…®zgi gumgi fara muuŇčgiap ki. Fhe Bak…®me nde muuŇčgim, nde Krais phorga taagia khavgiap, zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigim, Fhe Bak…®me nza fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana za nta vh…®zgi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Ef 2.14-16; 1 Pi 2.24\x*Fhe Bak…®me Moses ga n…®…®Ňčgi t…®vi, nta nza nzua nzuav, nza muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ndi k…®ra suav, nza nzuaim, nza ntan ŇčkasŇčkar piin ki. Fhe Bak…®me, nza nzuav nzuai buni, ana za nta vharav, ana nta vh…®zgi. Ana nta vh…®zgiap, ntan Krais khanarareŇč ga t…®ga fugi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Kor 1.13\x*Ana mba ŇčkasŇčka ki ŇčiniŇčgi, ana ntan ŇčkasŇčkagi vh…®zgiap, vh…®ra mba tori ŇčkasŇčkagi gu mbar…®vi ŇčkasŇčkagi, ana vh…®ra nta vh…®zgi. Krais ntorgap rimgi khanararen, Fhe Bak…®me khuen za mba gumgi kh…®vigi, ana za mba bigir ŇčkasŇčka vh…®zgiap, ana mba bigi ga muuŇčgim, kha gumgi gu mbigi nta kaŇčgi, nta za fhura ki bigi ma.
\s1 Nza Krais phorgap rimgim, mba Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi gu bigi, nta nzan kurarga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Ro 14.1-12; 1 Ko 8.8; Ga 4.10\x*Nde fhura guma the gan…®rim, ana bun thuen nde s…® khaŇč nde suaŇč thari, ‚ÄúNde mba gum mb…® pi t…®va z…®n vui fhu, nde rotu mbui tugi bak…®vi, nde nta z…®n vui fhu, nde k…®ni kama h…®gi tugar rotu mbui fhu, nde Sabatar rotu mbui fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Hi 8.5; 9.9; 10.1\x*Mba bigi, nta zumgum h…®rga big…®r ntuu ma. Krais, ana guigira big…®na guar ma.
\v 18 MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the ana r…®man kuv big…®n the gangip, ana bun nde suaŇčv khaŇč nde suanga, ‚ÄúNde wari mbevav, nde Fhe Bak…®me enseri rotur muuŇčri.‚ÄĚ Mba guma maaŇč nde suaŇčrim, nde fhura ana gan…®rim, ana nde mbev…® thari. Mba khesharigi gumgi, mbe wari won ndava vura nd…®knd…®gira z…®n vov, kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe nduarira guigira nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč ki.
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Ef 2.21; 4.15-16\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe guigira nza won guman pan Krais, mbe ana suira havhargi fhuvara. Mba pan, ana za mban won khar…®ga nd…®…®im, ana Ňčk…®riiŇč th…®vi, nta ana fhava phorgap nzerara ki. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana khar…®k, ana Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčkar, ana vuzvugar, ana vhuuva k…®vi.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Ga 4.3-5; 4.9\x*Nde Krais phorgap rimgi, nde wom kha buivar ki ŇčiniŇčgi gu nuianan ki tori gu mbar…®vi ŇčkasŇčkar piin ki fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde thaaŇč nzuav kha nuiana gumgi rui rurua mbui? Nde thaaŇč nzuav vh…®ra kha khesharigi t…®vi z…®n vui?
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt 1 T 4.3\x*‚ÄúNdu ana suig…® thari, ndu ana mb…® thari, ndu fhura ana gan…®rim, ana ndu fhava k…®zr…®g…® thari?‚ÄĚ
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Ais 29.13; Mt 15.9\x*Kha t…®vi, nta mba gu bigi ga nzuai. Nza nta mbegi, nta Ňčaar ki fhu. Mba bigi, nta vhemkora mbar…®gi bigi ma. Mba t…®vi, gumgi wari won nd…®knd…®gira nzuai t…®vi ma. Mbe ntan nza kh…®vav, nta z…®n Ňčg…®r zav nza nzuai.
\v 23 Guigira, mba khesharigi t…®vi, nta kha khesharigi. Mba t…®vi, nza kha ganganan nta mbui. Nta nzan muuŇčrim, nza enseri rotur muunga, nta nzan ndavi mbev…®rim, nza wari won fhavi vuzvugara z…®n Ňčg…®rga fhu. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gumgi mbari, mbe kha nd…®knd…®gar mba t…®vi ga mbui, nza nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč z…®n vui. Mba t…®vi, nta nzan kurav, nzan ndava vura t…®vi mbevarga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\c 3
\s1 Nza Krais phorga rimgiap, ana phorgap taagiap khavgi.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Sng 110.1; Mk 12.36; 16.19; Ef 1.20; Fi 1.30; Kor 1.29; 2.12; 1 Te 2.2\x*Krais rimgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagiap ana khavav, vh…®ra taagia nza khavgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza kha vun ki bigi, nza nta suaŇčv Ňčgar…®v, nta ndirga. Kha vun ki Ňčgun, Krais Fhe Bak…®men guva haren Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan pigi mpirmpir…®ga perav ki.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Mt 6.33\x*Nde zazera kha vun ki bigi ga nd…®knd…®g…®ri. Nde kha nuiana bigi ga nd…®knd…®g…® thari.
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Ro 6.2; 2 Ko 5.7; 5.14; Ga 2.20; Kor 2.20\x*Nde vh…®zgi gumgi fara muuŇčgiap, nden k…®r…® t…®vi gu bigi, nta Krais vhen zorgap, ana phorga kim, nde Fhe Bak…®me phorgap ki.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Zo 11.25; 14.6; 1 Ko 15.43; Fi 1.21; 1 Zo 3.2\x*Krais, ana nden k…®r…® t…®vi gu bigir n…®…®Ňčge ma. Krais ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me phorg…®p k…®rar h…®rga, nde vh…®ra ana phorg…®p k…®rga.
\ms1 Krais, ana nzan vhen kim, nza t…®vir Ňčkaa z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ma.
\s1 Nza t…®vir Ňčkaa z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ga gegi.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Ro 6.6; 6.11-13; 8.13; Ga 5.24; Ef 4.19; 5.3-5; 1 Te 4.5\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde kha nuianan t…®vi, nde won ndavi vherir za nta shogirim, nta rimgiri. Gu kha khesharigi t…®vi ga nzuai, nde ruarir gumgi gu mbigi wari ndi t…®v, nde ana thari, nde t…®vi mbat…®gi thari, nde ndavi khavav t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui t…®vi thari. Nde harigi gumgi bigi garav, nta niihi t…®vi thari. Harigi gumgi bigi garav nta niihi t…®v, ana mbar…®vi gu tori rotu mbui fara muuŇčgi.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Ef 5.6\x*Kha nuianan t…®vi mbat…®gi vuzvugap, Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daasui gumgi gu mbigi, Fhe Bak…®me mbe nzuav vheza mbat…®ga bevahegim, ana mbur ki. Ana mba vhezar mben n…®…®Ňčgirga.
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Ro 6.19-20; 1 Ko 6.11; Ef 2.2\x*Nde fhum vh…®ra mba gumgi gu mbigi phorga ruav, mba khesharigi t…®vi, nde za nta muuŇčgi.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Ef 4.22; 4.25-31; 5.4; Hi 12.1; 1 Pi 2.1\x*Nde ntigem, mba khesharigi t…®vi mbat…®gi, nde za nta vhararim, nta nde thav sari. Mba t…®vi mbari khare, vhegap, ndavi shiav, harigi gumgi ga nzuav ndavi mbar…®gi, buni mbat…®gir harigi gumgi ga nzuav, mbark…®rga buni mbat…®gi guarira nzuai.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Ef 4.22\x*Nde bevbevira, nde phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde mbe guiguig…® thari. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde mba ndava vura t…®vi, nde nta vharigim, nta nde thav sagi.
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Stt 1.26; Ro 12.2; Ef 2.10; 4.24\x*Nde t…®vir Ňčkaa ndigap, nta z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ma. Fhe Bak…®me nde muuŇčgim, nde t…®vir Ňčkaa z…®n vuim, ana zazera nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč vh…®rver nde nd…®…®v, nde muuŇčgim, nde t…®vir Ňčkaa z…®n vov guigira ana kaŇčgiap, nde ara fara muuŇčgir za mbui.
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Ro 10.12; Ga 3.28; Ef 1.23\x*Nza t…®vir Ňčkaa z…®n vui gumgi, nza za mba farara muuŇčgi. Nza kha nd…®knd…®gar muunga fhu, nza GrikiŇč ma, mbe ZudaiŇč ma, nza warir fooŇčgi nt…®…®ri ma, kheiŇč warir fooŇčgi fhuv nt…®…®ri ma, nza harigi khesharigi kaa nt…®…®ri ma, nza harigi fhaiŇč nt…®…®ri ma, nza fhura Ňčaara gumgi kh…®ni ma, nza b…®kb…®…®gi nt…®…®ri ma. Nza maaŇč suanga fhu. Krais, ana nduara za nzan vhen ki.
\s1 Nza guigira wari won ndavi wari ga nd…®…®i t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®rga.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Ga 5.22; Ef 4.32; Fi 2.1; 1 Pi 2.9\x*\x - \xo 3:12 \xt Ef 4.2\x*Fhe Bak…®me nden farasarigim, nde ana gumgi gu mbigi kim, ana guigira won ndavar nde n…®…®Ňčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde mba khesharigi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Nde guigira warir korar muuŇčv, t…®var vhuuŇčra warir muuŇčri. Nde guigira wari mbevav, nde mbarara harigi gumgi ga suaŇčv, t…®va mbat…®gen nde muuŇčgi guma, nde vhemkora ana suaŇčv ndav shi thari.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Mk 11.25; Ef 4.32; 5.2\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nden r…®gar, nde phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma the big…®na mbat…®ga thuen nde then muuŇčgirim, mba guma mba simt…®ga ndiv, ana ana muuŇčgi t…®va mbat…®geŇč, ana fhura ne nd…®knd…®k Ňčangip, ne nd…®knd…®gi thari. Guma Bak…®me, ana nde muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana nta vh…®zgiap, nta nd…®knd…®k Ňčangi. Mba t…®vara, nde phorg…®p guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma the nde muuŇčgi t…®va mbat…®geŇč, nde ne nd…®knd…®k Ňčangiri.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Ro 13.8-10; 1 Ko 13.13; Ef 4.3\x*Mba t…®vi, kha t…®v nta phorgi. Nde guigira wari won ndavir nde phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®Ňčri. Mba t…®v nza mbuim, nza wari t…®gap ndava bavira ki.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Ko 12.13; 12.27; Ef 2.16-17; 4.4; Fi 4.7\x*Krais, ana ndava m…®…®t…®gar nza nd…®…®v, nza mbuim, nza wari t…®gap ndava bavira kim, mba ndava m…®…®t…®k guigira nde ndavi gan…®rim, nde k…®ri. Fhe Bak…®me nden kamgim, nde wari t…®g…®p, ndava bavira k…®ri. Nde k…®v, zazera Fhe Bak…®men ndikndig…®p, ana phorg…® suaŇčri.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Ko 14.26; Ef 5.19; Kor 4.6\x*\x - \xo 3:16 \xt Ef 5.19-20\x*Nde fhura Krais buna vhuueŇč gan…®rim, ne khaŇč t…®g…®p nde ndavi vherir Ňčgar…®ri. Nde bevbevira, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde mbe phorg…® suaŇčv, nd…®knd…®gi vhuuin mbe kh…®v…®rim, mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčri. Nde Fhe Bak…®men ndikndig…®p wari won ndavi vherir ana phorg…®p suaŇčv, ana gavar Ňčgavi ki nde ntan muuŇčv, nde Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbui Ňčgavir muuŇčv, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nde ndavi khavim, nde ana rotu mbui Ňčgavi, nde ntan muuŇčri.
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Ko 10.31; Ef 5.20; 1 Te 5.18; Hi 13.15\x*Nde nzuai buni, nde mbui Ňčaari, gum nde mbui bigi zam, nde Guma Bak…®me Zisas z…®n panan za ntan muuŇčri. Nde ana z…®n, nde Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčv ana ndikndig…®ri.
\s1 Por guigira Zisas khoth…®gi ndegi gu ndegmbori ga nzuai.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Ef 5.22; Ta 2.5; 1 Pi 3.1\x*Nde mbigi, nde won mani piin k…®ri. Mba t…®v, ana Guma Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man nzerara.
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Ef 4.31; 5.25; 5.28; 1 Pi 3.7\x*Nde gumgi, nde vh…®ra guigira wari won ndavir wari won muuin n…®…®Ňčri. Nde mben muuŇčrim, mbe ndavi mbar…®g…® thari.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Ef 5.24; 6.1; Ta 2.9\x*Nde tari, nde wari won ndegi gu ndegmbori nzuai buni, nde zam nta mbararav, nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Guma Bak…®me mba t…®va vuzvugi.
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt Ef 6.4\x*Nde ndegi, nde wari won tarir muuŇčrim, mbe nden k…®n…® thari. Nde maaŇč muunga, mbe khueŇč nd…®knd…®g…®rga, mbe Ňčaara vhuuŇč then muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\s1 Por Ňčaara gumgi gum mbe gari mpiiŇčs…®gi ga nzuai.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt 1 T 6.1; Ta 2.9\x*\x - \xo 3:22 \xt Ef 6.5-8\x*Nde Ňčaara gumgi, nde wari wo gari mpiiŇčs…®gi nzuai buni, nde za nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Nde mben raaŇč sh…®v, mbe nde han k…®rim, nde mben r…®mgi vheri Ňčaarir muuŇč thari. Fhuvara. Nde Guma Bak…®men r…®v…®v, nde zazera guigira Ňčaara vhuuŇčra muuŇčri.
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt 1 Ko 7.22\x*Nde za mba bigir muuŇčv, nde khaŇč t…®g…®p ŇčkasŇčkagip mba bigir muuŇčri. Nde khaŇč suaŇč thari, ‚ÄúNza guman Ňčaara mbui.‚ÄĚ Fhuvara. Nde Guma Bak…®men Ňčaara mbui.
\v 24 Nde kaŇčgi, Guma Bak…®me zumgum vhezar nden n…®…®nga, ana mba bigir vhuuiŇč, ana ntan wo gumgi gu mbigir mbuigi nta ki. Nde khueŇč nd…®knd…®g…®ri, nde Kraisan Ňčaara gumgi ki, ana nduara nde gari mpiiŇčs…®ga guar ma.
\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt Lo 10.17; Ro 2.11; Ef 6.9; 1 Pi 1.17\x*Guma t…®va mbat…®geŇč muuŇčgi, ana mba t…®va mbat…®gen vheza ndirga. Fhe Bak…®me t…®va bavira z…®n vov, za kha gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga nzuav mbe nzuai.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Wkp 25.43; 25.53; Ef 6.9\x*Nde Ňčaara gari mpiiŇčs…®gi, nde t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p, nde t…®vir vhuuiŇčra wari won Ňčaari gumgir muuŇčri. Nde khueŇč kaŇčgi, nde vh…®ra, nde gari mpiiŇčs…®k, ana Hevenan ki.
\s1 Nza khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, tuituigira kha nuianan rui t…®v guigira havhargiri.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Ef 6.18; Fi 4.6\x*Nde Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai t…®v, nde ana suirav havhargiri. Nde maaŇč muuŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčv, nde nd…®knd…®gar vhuuŇčra muuŇčv, nde anan ndikndig…®p, ana phorg…®p suaŇčri.
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt Ro 15.30; 1 Ko 16.9; Ef 6.19\x*Nde Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčrim, ana vh…®ra nzan kurkurari. Nde ana phorg…®p suaŇčv ana nzarim, ana tuav fhog…®rim, nza Kraisan buna vhuueŇč bun suanga. Mba buna vhuueŇč, ne fhum zorga kegi, ne ntigem k…®rar h…®gi. Gumgi mbari mba buna vhuueŇč mbararargeŇč thagi. Mbe ne mbararargeŇč thav, na ndi b…®na kh…®ngi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Ef 6.20\x*Nde na suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčrim, gu tuituigip Fhe Bak…®me na vuzvugi t…®vara, gu mba buna vhuueŇč bun suanga.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Ef 5.15-16; 1 Te 4.11-12\x*Nde sios thav k…®rar ki gumgi han k…®v, nde nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p, nde t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčri. Nde zazera Krais t…®vara mbe kh…®v…®r saŇč muuŇčri.
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Mk 9.50; Ef 4.29; Kor 3.16; 1 Pi 3.15\x*Nde zazera mba gumgi mbararargeŇč vuzvugi bunin vhuuiŇčra suaŇčri. Nde nd…®knd…®ga vhuuŇčra muuŇčv harigi gumgi nzuai buni Ňčgarkari.
\s1 Por Tikikus gum Onesimus ga sarigim, mani Korosin vui.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt FG 20.4; 2 T 4.12\x*\x - \xo 4:7 \xt Ef 6.21-22\x*Tikikus ana mba gu mbui Ňčaari, ana za nta bun nde suanga. Tikikus, ana nza phorgap Ňčgarav, ana nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma ma. Nza guigira ana vuzvugi. Ana vh…®ra guigira Guma Bak…®men Ňčaara guman vhuuŇč ma.
\v 8 Gu mba big…®na n…®…®Ňčera nzuav, ana sarigim, ana nden han vui. Ana Ňčg…®p, nde suaŇčrim, nde nza ki k…®r…® t…®va kaŇčgir zav, nza ram mbui k…®r…® t…®va muuŇčgiap wari ki. Ana vh…®ra nde ndavi havhar…®rga.
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt Fm 1.10-12\x*Gu vh…®ra Onesimus ga sarigim, ana Tikikus phorga mbar vui. Onesimus, ana nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma ma. Ana vh…®ra guigira Zisas z…®n vui guma ma. Nza guigira ana vuzvugi. Ana vh…®ra nden k…®vntok ma. Mani khaŇč hi bigi, mani za nta bun nde suanga.\f a \fr 4:9 \ft Onesimus, ana Firemonan Ňčaara kh…®na mbui guma ma. Ndu Por Firemon ndi khergi gava gan…®. \f*
\s1 Por won raar vhuun KorosiŇč ga nd…®…®i.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt FG 12.12; 12.25; 13.13; 15.37-39; 19.29; 27.2; Fm 1.24\x*Aristarkus, ana na phorgap phena t…®vanan ki, ana won raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i. Mak, ana Barnabas Ňčguk ma, ana vh…®ra won raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgip Ňčg…®p, nden h…®rim, nde ana ndikndigip, gu khar nde nzuai kameŇč z…®n Ňčg…®p ana ndigiri.
\v 11 Zisas, mbe kha z…® phorgap anan kaai, Zastus, ana vh…®ra won raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i. Mbe ZudaiŇč r…®gar, mbe kha gumgira na phorgap Fhe Bak…®me won gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mbe ana piin k…®rga Ňčaara khavav, mbe kurkurar vhuun na mbui.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Kor 1.7; Fm 1.23\x*Epafras, ana vh…®ra won raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i. Ana nden k…®vntok ma, ana vh…®ra Krais Zisasan Ňčaara guma ma. Ana vh…®ra zazera khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap nde nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ana nden kurkurarim, nde khaŇč t…®g…® havhargip mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi farar muuŇčgip, nde guigira Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi kaŇčgip, guigira za ana vuzvugi kaŇčgirga.
\v 13 Gu khaŇč nde suan za mbui, ana khaŇč t…®gap Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav, nden kurkurav, vh…®ra kha Raodisia Ňčgu bak…®men ki siosan ki gumgi gu mbigir kurkurav, vh…®ra Hieraporis Ňčgu bak…®men ki siosan ki gumgi gu mbigi, ana vh…®ra mben kurkurigi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt 2 T 4.10-11; Fm 1.24\x*Ruk, nzan r…®…®i phenan Ňčgari guma, nza guigira ana vuzvugi. Mani Demas gum, wani won raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i.\f b \fr 4:14 \ft Gumgi vh…®rve kha nd…®knd…®ga ga mbui, Ruk nduara kha gava phuni khergi. Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč ki gap, Ruk ana fharigi ne, ana ana khergiap, Fhe Bak…®me farasarigi Ňčaari gumgi Ňčgarigi buni ki gap, Farsarigi Gumgi (Aposer) ana vh…®ra ana khergi. \f*
\p 
\v 15 Gu khueŇč vuzvugi, nde nan raar vhuuŇč ndiv, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Raodisia siosan ki, nde anan mbe n…®…®Ňčri. Nde vh…®ra nan raar vhuun Nimfar n…®…®Ňčv, vh…®ra ana phenan phogi ga vhui siosan ki gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®Ňčri.
\v 16 Nde kha gava gangip, nde vh…®ra ana ndiv, Raodisia Ňčgu bak…®men ki siosan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndi mbarari, mbe vh…®ra ana gangiri. Gu Raodisia siosan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndi mbarigi gap, nde vh…®ra ana gangiri.
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Fm 1.2\x*Nde khaŇč Arkipus ga suaŇčri, ‚ÄúNdu mba Guma Bak…®me han ndigi Ňčaar, ndu tuituigira ana gan…®v, ndu tuituigira ana muuŇčv, ana vh…®zgiri.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt 1 Ko 16.21; 2 Te 3.17\x*Gu Por, gu nduara kha raar vhuuŇč khergiap, nde ndi mbai. Nde na nd…®knd…®g…®ri, gu phena t…®vaneŇčra ki. Fhe Bak…®men fhura nden kora mbui kora muumbar nde phorg…® k…®ri. \fig Mbe shenin Por kegim, ana b…®nan ki. (4.18)|src="HK00203C.tif" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles/Louise Bass" ref="4.18"\fig*
